Tile is a layout manager for creating user interfaces in 32/64 bit Windows.

Features:

Unit tested controls
- seriously, how many UI frameworks are actually unit tested?
Weighted allocation of pixel space 
- gracefully fill the screen or contract to minimal space.
User editable theme
- Font
- Color
- Spacing
Flicker free display
- high update rates possible
Controls
- Button
- Edit
- Combo
- Tree
Generic Container
- Flow
Type-Aware Container
- List
- Grid
